		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>With Cleveland's spring thaw approaching, proactively test your sump pump by pouring a bucket of water into the pit to ensure it activates and drains properly. If it fails to engage or makes unusual noises, promptly contact a professional to avoid potential basement flooding.</p>
